Title: Death Knell
Plot: Earth's secret offworld base is attacked by Anubis' forces, and Major Carter finds herself being hunted by the enemy. General Hammond and Jacob Carter make an unnerving discovery about the Earth-Tok'ra alliance.
GuestStars: Sebastian Spence, Dan Payne, Mark Gibbon, Gary Jones, Nels Lennarson, Eric Breker, Sam MacMillan
